    "description": "通过“不滚动的单屏幕战斗”、“武器的炫目支援攻击”和“美丽的3D图形”来吸引玩家。<br>一定要尝试新感觉的双摇杆射击游戏『XALADIA』！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/2d4fa08dbe8825649438b6912b101576.poster.avif?t=1734325132\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/2d4fa08dbe8825649438b6912b101576.webm?t=1734325132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/2d4fa08dbe8825649438b6912b101576.mp4?t=1734325132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏设定</h2>你作为星球调查队的特勤士兵，为了银河行星的调查任务和开发，巡游于许多星球之间。<br>然而，突然有敌人出现阻挡了你的任务。<br>这支庞大的军队覆盖了整个宇宙，由来自极好战的银河强国的外星人组成。<br><br>总部向你下达命令，决定为了保护星球而战。<br>“在支援星球开发的同时，消灭敌人并返回地球（基地）。”<br>21世纪初，人类和外星人之间的宇宙霸权争夺战开始了。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >XALADIA的特点</h2>-不滚动的单屏幕战斗<br><br>-使用各种武器的炫目支援攻击<br>-美丽的3D图形<br>-士兵本身以及枪支、制造武器的能力提升<br>-每次玩都会有不同的星球和敌人出现模式的阶段生成系统<br>-射击游戏融合了复古感和现代的视觉和系统<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不滚动的单屏幕战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/6add5e0245a78f6ef9d125fb2c637e3f.poster.avif?t=1734325132\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/6add5e0245a78f6ef9d125fb2c637e3f.webm?t=1734325132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/6add5e0245a78f6ef9d125fb2c637e3f.mp4?t=1734325132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在单屏幕中进行战斗，玩家可以自由移动屏幕内并与外星人作战。<br>当战斗在屏幕内变得激烈时，速度和现场感会增强。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器的炫目支援攻击</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/3140396bbd8ec481c6997a246434fd8b.poster.avif?t=1734325132\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/3140396bbd8ec481c6997a246434fd8b.webm?t=1734325132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/3140396bbd8ec481c6997a246434fd8b.mp4?t=1734325132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>除了玩家装备的武器外，还有可以进行支援攻击的武器。<br>通过放置多个武器，对外星人的攻击会变得更加炫目。<br>根据武器的种类和性能，可以进行不同的攻击，画面中充满了爆炸、激光、导弹等。<br><br>另外，还有提高自己能力值和武器能力值，可以爽快地消灭敌人的元素。<br>因此，可以享受更高效和流畅的游戏体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >美丽的3D图形</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/a517a17d09b3e508e2ca8b9aa7466a92.poster.avif?t=1734325132\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/a517a17d09b3e508e2ca8b9aa7466a92.webm?t=1734325132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218190/extras/a517a17d09b3e508e2ca8b9aa7466a92.mp4?t=1734325132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>深度感十足的背景、精致的光影和效果，制作团队在细节上的用心打磨，创造了一个美丽而有力的视觉体验。<br><br><br>XALADIA is the first self-published release from the developers of Tenchu, Way of the Samurai, AKIBA’S TRIP, and the Octopath Traveler series.",
